      <Content>&lt;p&gt;Written using WinRT, running in a sandbox&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;Deployment of apps:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Need a dev licence to stop the community from ‘side loading’ apps outside of the app store &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Store &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;In enterprise can use Group Policy to allow side loaded apps &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;WinRT only tablets can be certified?      &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Windows8_9AE6/image_4.png"&gt;&lt;img title="image" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Windows8_9AE6/image_thumb_1.png" width="626" height="245" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Windows8_9AE6/image_2.png"&gt;&lt;img title="image" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Windows8_9AE6/image_thumb.png" width="225" height="244" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;     &lt;br /&gt;Sample generated from template Grid Application template&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Windows8_9AE6/image_6.png"&gt;&lt;img title="image" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Windows8_9AE6/image_thumb_2.png" width="600" height="385" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;     &lt;br /&gt;Viewing the app in the simulator&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;Observable collections&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Windows8_9AE6/image_30.png"&gt;&lt;img title="image" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Windows8_9AE6/image_thumb_14.png" width="541" height="360" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;     &lt;br /&gt;The CollectionViewSource called groupedItemsViewSource&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;**class diagram and flow of app put in.. Why sealed?&amp;#160; try to Simplify model.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;h3&gt;2. Collections and Groupings&lt;/h3&gt;  &lt;p&gt;ListView and GridView    &lt;br /&gt;Both derived from ItemsControl&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;Can populate an ItemsControl by adding items directly to its items collection or by binding its ItemsSource property to a data source.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Windows8_9AE6/image_8.png"&gt;&lt;img title="image" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Windows8_9AE6/image_thumb_3.png" width="442" height="380" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;Adding in the webservice call in SampleDataSource.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Windows8_9AE6/image_10.png"&gt;&lt;img title="image" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Windows8_9AE6/image_thumb_4.png" width="555" height="314" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&amp;#160; &lt;br /&gt;Data is returned back using async, which means it loads up in front the of the user.&amp;#160; Very nice.&amp;#160; Seems to be passed back as the ObservableCollection of AllGroups.&amp;#160; Which is bound to the UI.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;**TODO – make simplest possible observable collection, maybe using flickr.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;h3&gt;3. Animation and Styling&lt;/h3&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Windows8_9AE6/image_12.png"&gt;&lt;img title="image" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Windows8_9AE6/image_thumb_5.png" width="547" height="309" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;     &lt;br /&gt;Putting rounded corners on the pictures and made changes to the overlay too.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;h3&gt;Changing App Title and Logo&lt;/h3&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Windows8_9AE6/image_14.png"&gt;&lt;img title="image" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Windows8_9AE6/image_thumb_6.png" width="487" height="418" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;     &lt;br /&gt;appmanifest file.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Windows8_9AE6/image_20.png"&gt;&lt;img title="image" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Windows8_9AE6/image_thumb_9.png" width="492" height="278" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Windows8_9AE6/image_18.png"&gt;&lt;img title="image" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Windows8_9AE6/image_thumb_8.png" width="334" height="298" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Windows8_9AE6/image_16.png"&gt;&lt;img title="image" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Windows8_9AE6/image_thumb_7.png" width="479" height="271" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;     &lt;br /&gt;Putting on entrance transition for the ItemDetail screen.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;h3&gt;4. Controls and Views&lt;/h3&gt;  &lt;p&gt;adding an app bar&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Windows8_9AE6/image_22.png"&gt;&lt;img title="image" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Windows8_9AE6/image_thumb_10.png" width="516" height="292" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;adding a basic control into the detail page:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Windows8_9AE6/image_24.png"&gt;&lt;img title="image" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Windows8_9AE6/image_thumb_11.png" width="383" height="206" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;     &lt;br /&gt;This is what we want for the details page.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Windows8_9AE6/image_26.png"&gt;&lt;img title="image" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Windows8_9AE6/image_thumb_12.png" width="481" height="272" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;     &lt;br /&gt;Completed view&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;h3&gt;5. Settings&lt;/h3&gt;  &lt;p&gt;Adding in a settings charm extension which writes to local settings&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Windows8_9AE6/image_28.png"&gt;&lt;img title="image" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Windows8_9AE6/image_thumb_13.png" width="518" height="259" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;     &lt;br /&gt;User will be able to set the number of photos retrieved in preferences, settings&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;**Is this supposed to remember settings between ‘instances’&lt;/p&gt;</Content>
